net.rk4z.mcef.MCEF

Serializable, Comparable<MCEF>, Constable
public enum MCEF extends Enum<MCEF>
An API to create Chromium web browsers in Minecraft. Uses a modified version of java-cef (Java Chromium Embedded Framework).
